-- Immediate-Delivery Gold Drops From Record, Falls 0.4% to $1,386.75/Ounce
-- B y   S u n g w o o   P a r k
-- 2010-11-05T00:39:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-05/immediate-delivery-gold-drops-from-record-falls-0-4-to-1-386-75-ounce.html
Gold for immediate delivery declined
as much as 0.4 percent to $1,386.75 an ounce, dropping from a
record $1,394.41 an ounce touched earlier today. The precious
metal traded at $1,387.07 an ounce at 8:36 a.m. in Singapore.  To contact the reporter on this story:
